Docker Hub Private

@@ Without Secret:
ImagePullBackOff

@@ With Secret:
Image Downloads Successfully

#########################################
############# Secret Rotation ##########
@@ Current Password:
oldpassword

@@ Security team changes to:
newpassword

@@ Update Secret:
[root@k8s-control01 ~]# kubectl edit secret db-secret
or
[root@k8s-control01 ~]# kubectl apply -f secret.yaml

@@ Restart Deployment:
[root@k8s-control01 ~]# kubectl rollout restart deployment mysql-app

@@ Production Requirement:
Rotate passwords regularly

